<scenario>
The agent A provided the following violation scenario:
In the provided project configuration MHD_TCP_CORK_NOPUSH is defined (via #define MHD_TCP_CORK_NOPUSH TCP_CORK). The shown fragment is inside the #else /* ! MHD_TCP_CORK_NOPUSH */ branch, so that branch is never included in any translation unit built with these defines. Therefore that fragment cannot be compiled or executed in this project configuration — it is dead/unreachable code.
</scenario>
